      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are solid, the exterior shows some age with minor dings and paint fading in certain areas. The interior is clean but has some visible wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a great option for someone looking for a functional car who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
