    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and consistent care. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and safety. Featuring a refined interior and a robust service history, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to experience the superior road manners and enduring value of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34850.0,
